ls of reionization, galaxy formation and chemical\nevolution in order to consider these galaxies forming prior to reionization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Aug 2014 20:00:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Sep 2014 18:54:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
