wing-angle dependence of the emerging spectrum, as a\nfunction of rotational velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Aug 2014 21:20:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Sep 2014 16:21:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
